Text: Person that put her life on hold, betrayal, anger, unhappy, love and letting
  go and starting lover and finding peace and finding a sanctuary were her family
  can be safe and be happy and play and be free and not be in a place were they can't
  be them self everything they do it feels like they in prison because they are been
  watch, blackmail, death threats, talk behind their backs etc. People that try anything
  to get rid of them so long they get what they want. They don't care who they hurt
  or walk over so long they get it. Or use.
